/>\n但係基本上都係慢慢感受旅程，連景點都唔多會去"},{"pid":"06c34653018b1d5801835cc008514a8464360c47","tid":783880,"uid":141782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"上次有條友問西班牙一日預一二千夠唔夠<br />\n另一件衝出黎話洗鬼洗咁多咩 去超級市場五歐買d 火腿面包夠食五日啦<br />\n心諗去旅行食到咁去黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cac2e9af540d0706a44bbacbee270af34a0dac4","tid":783880,"uid":156948,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係麻撚煩 乜鳩都係到反係到嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d8ae154e446cf96d7d079ba09d79b795fd4ebf","tid":783880,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"樓主好啱，唔跟你個標準去做一件事就一定要批評。<br />\n<br />\n我已知道樓主係存在的。"},{"pid":"8fe87fc087976ecb9e49a8cbc4c6ce02ee766b71","tid":783880,"uid":50500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"fb3f42185069128861b9d1488858bf76d82a766d","tid":783880,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"標題內文不符 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a78d33ca19ce0e4bea1a5fa9f7815ea7107e51","tid":783880,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"你嗰啲叫on9遊喎，我細個無錢都係慳住玩，但完全無做過你所講啲鳩嘢。"},{"pid":"e3480920fad4875d0375b5da98e56b4805768fb3","tid":783880,"uid":988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"窮游ok，但係去旅行 R人地當地人爛腳仲要老奉咁就唔好啦"},{"pid":"25d22533024c5d134d620c0615f405a28dcdaf1e","tid":783880,"uid":75123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬你講嗰啲唔係窮遊喎"},{"pid":"7531274a6694800cb65f3fde30eb3b1285e1fbef","tid":783880,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16: